<div class="profile-info container text-center">
  <div class="row justify-content-start">
    <div class="col-md-6 text-left">
      <h1>Account Info</h1>

      <div class="card-user" style="width: 30rem; margin: auto;">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1632498301446-5f78baad40d0?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8Mnx8ZG9nJTIwb3duZXJ8ZW58MHx8MHx8fDA%3D" class="img-thumbnail rounded mx-auto d-block" style="width: 50%;"/>
        <div class="card-user-infos">
          <% if @user %>
            <p class="text-center">Emily</p>
            <p>London</p>
            <p>Hello pet-loving community! I'm Emily, and my beloved four-legged companion is Max, the ultimate jetsetter pup. As we embark on our next adventure, I'm on the lookout for the perfect pet-sitter to provide a warm and loving home for Max while I'm away. If you're someone who understands the importance of cuddles, playtime, and a little wanderlust, join us in making sure Max has the best staycation ever! Your home could be the perfect pitstop for Max's vacation. Let's chat and ensure a tail-wagging experience</p>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="booking-info container text-center">
  <h2>Bookings:</h2>
    <ul>
      <% @bookings.each do |booking| %>
        <li>
          <p>Booking ID: <%= booking.id %></p>
          <p>Start Date: <%= booking.date_from %></p>
          <p>End Date: <%= booking.date_to %></p>
          <p>Comment: <%= booking.comment %></p>
        </li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
</div>
